data.description: Lovely two story home with many updates. Three bedrooms and two full bathrooms upstairs. Convenient upstairs laundry and half bath downstairs. Two car garage and a large private fenced backyard with stone patio and pergola to relax and entertain. New floors throughout the first floor and upstairs bathrooms. Remodeled kitchen with stainless appliances and nice large walk in pantry. Large living room and dining area. Roomy master bedroom with vaulted ceilings and large garden tub in master bath. Close to I-485, I-85, shopping, concerts, restaurants, and so much more.
